      <h2>We wanted a better mattress and a better buying experience</h2>
      <p>Loom & Leaf was born out of the success of our innerspring mattress, Saatva. Saatva was a place where we discovered people like ourselves -- people who did not think it was too much to ask to get the best nights' sleep on a luxury mattress without the cost, drama, and hassle of mattress shopping in stores.</p>
