            <p>We are not only committed to giving customers a better nights’ sleep and a better buying experience, we are equally passionate about our planet and our communities. For us, it’s not enough to be good at what you do. The real proof of character is in giving back to those in need. In the last year we have donated hundreds of mattresses and partnered with over 10 organizations.</p>
            <p>Recently, we partnered with the Seeds of Hope organization to provide 50 free mattresses to help the victims of Hurricane Sandy along the Jersey Shore. As many of you know, the shorelines and communities along New Jersey and New York were destroyed by Hurricane Sandy, leaving many families without a home or a place to sleep. As many families struggled to rebuild, we wanted to make sure they didn’t have the added stress and expense of trying to buy a decent mattress in addition to everything else. It was the least we could do.</p>
